snippet.title: Atomic Butcher gameplay
snippet.description:
Atomic Butcher in meatworld - gameplay footage of upcoming ultra-violent, over the top platformer/360° - shooter "Atomic Butcher: Homo Metabolicus", release date set for early August!

Check out our Homepage at atomicbutcher.info, we also have a playable demo at http://www.atomicbutcher.info/media/!
The Atomic Butcher is fighting his way through a ruined city and evades explosive traps. Listen to another soundbyte from the OST!

Follow us on
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/atomicbutcher
Twitter: https://twitter.com/atomic_butcher
Steam: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=650695447
